<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head') %></head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav', { user, activePage: 'whats-new' }) %>
  <main class="simple-page legal-page">
    <a href="<%= user ? '/dashboard' : '/login' %>" class="breadcrumb-back">&larr; Back</a>
    <h2>What's New</h2>

    <div class="whats-new-entry">
      <div class="whats-new-date">Latest</div>
      <h3>Professional Profile &amp; Account Menu <span class="new-tag">NEW</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>New Profile page: add your professional title, summary, skills, and experience — or upload your resume to auto-fill it via AI. You always review and confirm before anything saves.</li>
        <li>New account menu with quick links to Profile, Settings, Help, and FAQ.</li>
        <li>Settings page now includes a light/dark theme toggle that applies instantly across the whole app.</li>
        <li>New Help documentation and FAQ pages to get you up to speed faster.</li>
        <li>Dashboard decluttered: milestone perk cards are now compact and side-by-side, and the "Coming Soon" carousel auto-cycles through all upcoming features.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="whats-new-entry">
      <h3>Referral &amp; Gamification System</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Invite friends via your unique referral link to unlock rewards: 1 referral unlocks the AI Interview Simulator, 3 referrals unlock VIP AI Resume Matcher access, and 5 referrals earns you the "Ghostbuster" badge.</li>
        <li>Each referral also grants +5 application storage slots (Capacity Expansion widget on your dashboard).</li>
        <li>New floating "Share App" button on the dashboard makes it easy to grab your invite link anytime.</li>
        <li>Celebratory toast + confetti animation when a friend joins using your link.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="whats-new-entry">
      <h3>Polish &amp; UX Improvements <span class="new-tag">NEW</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>More visible, lively floating-ghost 👻 micro-animation across the app.</li>
        <li>Global toast notifications and button loading-spinners for a smoother, more responsive feel on every action.</li>
        <li>Mobile-friendly touch targets, stacked forms, and swipeable Kanban board on small screens.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="whats-new-entry">
      <h3>Magic Upload</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Upload a screenshot of your application confirmation and auto-fill Company &amp; Role.</li>
        <li>Upload a PDF of your sent application email and auto-fill Company &amp; Role.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="whats-new-entry">
      <h3>Inbound Email Auto-Tracking <span class="new-tag">NEW</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Forward your application confirmation emails and we'll automatically add them to your board.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="whats-new-entry">
      <h3>Account &amp; Security <span class="new-tag">NEW</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Terms &amp; Conditions and Privacy Policy pages added, linked from Sign-Up.</li>
        <li>Improved navigation with a shared top nav and breadcrumb back-links across the app.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
